This project involves creating a professional digital portfolio using platforms like GitHub, LinkedIn, and Kaggle. Each platform serves a unique purpose: GitHub showcases technical projects, LinkedIn highlights professional and academic information, and Kaggle supports data science practice.

I set up and updated my profiles, created a GitHub README portfolio, and ensured my LinkedIn education details are complete. Screenshots were taken as proof of completion.

Over time, I plan to keep these platforms updated with new projects, skills, and achievements to build a strong online presence and improve career opportunities.
